{"tid":2361900,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"到底啲中老年中層係咪全部都心理變態？","createTime":"2021-01-11T05:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T16:51:36.000Z","uid":348098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f26c8774e1f3a7be9f4596ec69a35a6112e1ee4","tid":2361900,"uid":348098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"話說最近高層想assign個大pj俾我跟<br />\n條中年叔伯就係度放暗箭話信唔過我<br />\n想叫高層俾個pj俾另外同我同期嘅同事跟<br />\n擺明想借啲意踢走我啦<br />\n平是都已經成日將我啲野俾其他人做<br />\n不過好彩大老細都係鐘意我多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅持要俾我跟<br />\n最有問題係佢唔覺得自己有問題<br />\n全世界都錯佢就啱哂<br />\n成鬼日都係度單單打打<br />\n人前笑笑口懶係有禮貌咁<br />\n人後就瘋狂篤背脊講壞話<br />\n平時我都配合下笑下就算<br />\n今次真係好想大巴大巴煎死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴線仲八婆過啲老處女上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450f34731b87cf15ddbb32e2b98de384480dfb42","tid":2361900,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"通常得閒無野做果d老屎忽最鐘意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df0d32ec3971a1ce8a6b6501c6dbc690da15096","tid":2361900,"uid":98037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"公司個老屎忽都係咁，持住做得耐啲就扮代表指指點點，嫌三嫌四，麻撚煩"},{"pid":"a0367a079d2a863c00aaa72c953aa21b0fe2c70f","tid":2361900,"uid":348098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"450f34731b87cf15ddbb32e2b98de384480dfb42","tid":2361900,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"通常得閒無野做果d老屎忽最鐘意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:56:43.000Z","msg":"成日返到嚟淨係識得指手畫腳<br />\n野又唔見佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b10cd478ea8d6465605c78055040cf0ead069","tid":2361900,"uid":348098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5df0d32ec3971a1ce8a6b6501c6dbc690da15096","tid":2